title: 15 MIN TABATA AB Workout - No Repeat Exercises, Tabata Cardio Style, Low Impact
description:
NEW Tabata Workout! Are you ready for a 15 MIN Tabata Ab Burner? Super fun + super effective! All you need is 15 minutes and your mat 💪🏼 Let's strengthen our core muscles together team! Don't stop when you feel your core shake... embrace the burn! Let's do it! 🔥

▸ Muscles Worked: Total Core Burner
▸ Time: 15 Min
▸ Equipment: No Equipment

▸ Instructions: Follow along and complete as many reps as possible in 20 Seconds. After 10 Seconds of Rest continue to the next move.

▸ The Workout:
1. Tabata Workout 0:00 - 13:05
2. Cool Down 13:13 - 16:24

Please remember that we are all different and that you can make this your own workout ♡ Take a longer break when you need to.
